  "summary": "Jenkins HTML Publisher Plugin has a XSS vulnerability in the legacy wrapper file",
  "details": "Jenkins HTML Publisher Plugin versoins 427 and earlier do not escape the job name and URL in the legacy wrapper file.\n\nThis results in a stored cross-site scripting (XSS) vulnerability exploitable by attackers with Item/Configure permission.\n\nHTML Publisher Plugin 427.1 escapes job name and URL when generating the legacy wrapper file.",
